Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.47,0:00:15.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,坦格利安王朝的第一个世纪\N{\fs16}As the first century of the Targaryen dynasty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.27,0:00:16.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,已近尾声\N{\fs16}came to a close
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.02,0:00:21.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,人瑞王杰赫里斯一世的身体状况每况愈下\N{\fs16}the health of the Old King, Jaehaerys, was failing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.07,0:00:28.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那段岁月里 坦格利安家族轭下尚有十条成年巨龙\N{\fs16}In those days, House Targaryen stood at the height of its strength
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.74,0:00:31.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,家族势力如日中天\N{\fs16}with ten adult dragons under its yoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:35.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,世间无人可与之抗衡\N{\fs16}No power in the world could stand against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.50,0:00:39.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,杰赫里斯国王的统治近六十年\N{\fs16}King Jaehaerys reigned over nearly 60 years
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.13,0:00:41.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王国和平而繁荣\N{\fs16}of peace and prosperity
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:44.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,未曾想悲剧夺走了他的长子和次子的性命\N{\fs16}but tragedy had claimed both his sons
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:46.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,使得继承人成了疑问\N{\fs16}leaving his succession in doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.13,0:00:49.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,于是在征服101年\N{\fs16}So, in the year 101
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.68,0:00:53.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,人瑞王召开大议会来选定继承人\N{\fs16}the Old King called a Great Council to choose an heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.35,0:00:58.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,上千领主赶赴赫伦堡\N{\fs16}Over a thousand lords made the journey to Harrenhal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.77,0:01:02.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,十四位继承人选参与听证\N{\fs16}Fourteen succession claims were heard
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.36,0:01:06.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但真正的竞争者只有两位\N{\fs16}but only two were truly considered.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.11,0:01:10.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮丝·坦格利安公主 国王最年长的后裔\N{\fs16}Princess Rhaenys Targaryen, the King's eldest descendant
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.95,0:01:14.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,和她的堂弟 韦赛里斯·坦格利安王子\N{\fs16}and her younger cousin, Prince Viserys Targaryen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.70,0:01:17.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王最年长的男性后裔\N{\fs16}the King's eldest male descendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.67,0:01:27.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,七大王国所有大小领主\N{\fs16}It is declared by all lords paramount
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.67,0:01:32.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,和下属封臣共同宣布\N{\fs16}and lords vassal of the Seven Kingdoms
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.39,0:01:39.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,韦赛里斯·坦格利安王子获封龙石岛亲王！\N{\fs16}that Prince Viserys Targaryen be made Prince of Dragonstone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.23,0:01:45.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮丝身为女人 无缘继承铁王座\N{\fs16}Rhaenys, a woman, would not inherit the Iron Throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.11,0:01:50.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,领主们选择了韦赛里斯\N{\fs16}The lords instead chose Viserys
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.03,0:01:53.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的父亲\N{\fs16}my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.79,0:01:58.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,杰赫里斯召开大议会\N{\fs16}Jaehaerys called the Great Council
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.96,0:02:02.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,避免了因继承权而掀起战争\N{\fs16}to prevent a war being fought over his succession.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.63,0:02:04.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,只因他知晓那个冷酷的真相\N{\fs16}For he knew the cold truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.79,0:02:09.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,能摧毁龙王家族的\N{\fs16}The only thing that could tear down the House of the Dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.88,0:02:11.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,只有它自己\N{\fs16}was itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:05.62,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,听话 叙拉克斯！\N{\fs16}Dohaerās, Syrax!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:10.50,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fs16}Umbās.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:13.05,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,乖！\N{\fs16}Rȳbās!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.02,0:04:28.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 公主 相信您骑得很过瘾\N{\fs16}Welcome back, Princess. I trust your ride was pleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:30.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,别故作轻松了 爵士\N{\fs16}Try not to look too relieved, ser.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:31.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我是真的轻松\N{\fs16}I am relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:34.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,每次那只金色巨兽带您安然无恙地回来\N{\fs16}Every time that golden beast brings you back unspoiled
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.78,0:04:36.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的脑袋又逃过一次枪尖\N{\fs16}it saves my head from a spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:39.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,叙拉克斯长得很快\N{\fs16}Syrax is growing quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:41.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她很快就和科拉克休一样大了\N{\fs16}She'll soon be as large as Caraxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.08,0:04:44.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,大到可以放上双人龙鞍\N{\fs16}That's almost large enough to saddle two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.12,0:04:47.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我确信我在一旁当个观众就很满足了 谢谢\N{\fs16}I believe I'm quite content as a spectator, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.17,0:04:52.21,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,听话\N{\fs16}Dohaerās.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.75,0:04:54.80,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,往前！\N{\fs16}Naejot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.68,0:06:24.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉\N{\fs16}Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.14,0:06:27.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你知道我现在这个情况下\N{\fs16}You know I don't like you to go flying
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.89,0:06:29.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不喜欢你去骑龙\N{\fs16}while I'm in this condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.52,0:06:31.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你在任何情况下都不喜欢我骑龙\N{\fs16}You don't like me to go flying while you're in any condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.90,0:06:36.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 王后陛下 - 早 阿莉森\N{\fs16}- Your Grace. - Good morrow, Alicent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:38.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你睡了吗？\N{\fs16}Did you sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:40.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 睡了 - 睡了多久？\N{\fs16}- I slept. - How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.45,0:06:43.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不需要你来当老妈 雷妮拉\N{\fs16}I don't need mothering, Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:45.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但你周围这些服侍的人\N{\fs16}Well, here you are, surrounded by attendants
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:47.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,都只关心你肚子里的宝宝\N{\fs16}all focused on the babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:50.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,总得有人关心你\N{\fs16}Someone has to attend to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:55.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,很快你也会躺在这张床上 雷妮拉\N{\fs16}You will lie in this bed soon enough, Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:59.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这种煎熬就是我们服务王国的方式\N{\fs16}This discomfort is how we serve the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.76,0:07:02.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我宁愿身为骑士驰骋疆场 去赢得荣誉\N{\fs16}I'd rather serve as a knight and ride to battle and glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:08.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们的子宫属于王室 你和我都是\N{\fs16}We have royal wombs, you and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:12.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,产床就是我们的战场\N{\fs16}The childbed is our battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:16.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们必须学会咬牙面对\N{\fs16}We must learn to face it with a stiff lip.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.40,0:07:20.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在去洗个澡\N{\fs16}Now take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:22.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你臭得像条龙\N{\fs16}You stink of dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:25.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,于是我对他说 我相信你\N{\fs16}So, I said to him, "Well, I believe
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.99,0:07:28.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,应该看看另一端\N{\fs16}you might be looking up the wrong end."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:33.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,大人们\N{\fs16}My lords.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:35.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,自由贸易城邦的联盟正在壮大\N{\fs16}The growing alliance among the Free Cities
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:38.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,开始自称三女儿王国\N{\fs16}has taken to styling itself the Triarchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.59,0:07:40.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们在血石岛聚集\N{\fs16}They have massed on Bloodstone
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.80,0:07:42.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,目前正在驱除盘踞在石阶列岛\N{\fs16}and are presently ridding the Stepstones
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.47,0:07:43.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,的那些海盗\N{\fs16}of its pirate infestation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:46.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,听起来倒像是个好消息 科利斯大人\N{\fs16}Well, that sounds suspiciously like good news, Lord Corlys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:48.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有个叫克拉哈斯·达哈尔的家伙\N{\fs16}A man called Craghas Drahar
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:51.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,自称三女儿王国的海军上将亲王\N{\fs16}has styled himself the prince-admiral of this Triarchy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:54.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,别人叫他螃蟹喂食者\N{\fs16}They call him the Crabfeeder
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.56,0:07:58.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,缘于他颇有创意的处死敌人的方式\N{\fs16}due to his inventive methods of punishing his enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:00.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,难道我们要为海盗们哀悼吗？\N{\fs16}And are we meant to weep for dead pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.69,0:08:04.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 不 陛下 - 雷妮拉 你迟到了\N{\fs16}- No, Your Grace. - Rhaenyra, you're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:05.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王的侍酒可不能迟到\N{\fs16}The King's cupbearer must not be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.99,0:08:08.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 大人们都渴了 - 我去看望母亲了\N{\fs16}- Leaves people wanting for cups. - I was visiting Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:12.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,骑龙去的？\N{\fs16}On dragonback?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.29,0:08:15.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下 戴蒙王子一直敦促国库\N{\fs16}Hey, Your Grace, at Prince Daemon's urging
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:18.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,拨巨款给他的都城守备队\N{\fs16}the crown has invested significant capital
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:22.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,以加强训练和升级装备\N{\fs16}in the re-training and re-equipping of his City Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.09,0:08:26.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我认为您也应该敦促您弟弟出席御前会议\N{\fs16}I thought you might urge your brother to fill his seat on the council
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:29.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,作为都城守备队队长\N{\fs16}and provide an assessment of his progress
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.26,0:08:31.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,向我们汇报工作进度\N{\fs16}as commander of the Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:33.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你不觉得戴蒙现在沉迷于工作\N{\fs16}Do you think Daemon is distracted by his present tasks?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:36.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,既能释放精力 又无暇他顾也不错吗？\N{\fs16}And that his thoughts and energies are occupied?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.14,0:08:39.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,希望如此 毕竟我们付出了不少成本\N{\fs16}Well, one would hope so, considering the associated costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:42.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那就当你花的钱是笔划算的投资吧 毕斯柏里大人\N{\fs16}Then let us all consider your gold well-invested, Lord Beesbury.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:45.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我认为您不能再纵容三女儿王国\N{\fs16}I would urge that you not allow this Triarchy much latitude
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.99,0:08:47.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在石阶列岛为所欲为了 陛下\N{\fs16}in the Stepstones, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:51.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一旦航道受阻 会让我们的港口难以为继\N{\fs16}If those shipping lanes should fall, it will beggar our ports.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:54.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王已经听到你的谏言了 科利斯大人\N{\fs16}The crown has heard your report, Lord Corlys
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:56.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,会认真考虑的\N{\fs16}and takes it under advisement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:05.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们来谈谈王储比武大会吧 陛下\N{\fs16}Shall we discuss the Heir's Tournament, Your Grace?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:07.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我十分乐意\N{\fs16}I would be delighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.05,0:09:10.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,学士们预测的命名日可靠吗 梅罗斯\N{\fs16}Will the maesters' name day prediction hold, Mellos?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.14,0:09:13.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您要明白这毕竟只是预测 陛下\N{\fs16}You must understand that these things are mere estimations, my King
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.81,0:09:17.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但我们在月表上呕心沥血\N{\fs16}but we have all been poring over the moon charts
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.27,0:09:21.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,相信我们的预测已经尽可能精确\N{\fs16}and we feel that our forecast is as accurate as it can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.11,0:09:23.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,比武大会的开销巨大\N{\fs16}The cost of the tournament is not negligible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:28.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,或许我们可以推迟至孩子出生后再开始？\N{\fs16}Perhaps we might delay until the child is in hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:29.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,大多数领主和骑士\N{\fs16}Most of the lords and knights
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.82,0:09:31.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,都已经在赶往君临的路上\N{\fs16}are certainly on their way to King's Landing already.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.66,0:09:32.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 现在让他们回去…… - 比武大会将持续\N{\fs16}- To turn them back now... - The tourney will take
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.95,0:09:34.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,大半个星期\N{\fs16}the better part of a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:37.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在比武大会结束前  我儿子便出生了\N{\fs16}Before the games are over, my son will be born
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.54,0:09:39.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,整个国家将为之庆祝\N{\fs16}and the whole realm will celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.25,0:09:42.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们还无法预测孩子的性别\N{\fs16}We have no way of predicting the sex of the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:45.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当然 没有学士会在缺乏依据的情况下\N{\fs16}Of course, no maester's capable of rendering an opinion
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:46.76,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,做出判断 是吧？\N{\fs16}free of conditions, are they now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:49.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王后肚子里怀的是男孩\N{\fs16}There's a boy in the Queen's belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.76,0:09:51.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs16}I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:55.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而我的继承人很快就会\N{\fs16}And my heir will soon put all of this
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.14,0:09:57.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,亲自平息这一切糟心事\N{\fs16}damnable hand-wringing to rest himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.73,0:10:03.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,天一亮他就穿过了红堡大门\N{\fs16}He passed through the Red Keep's gates at first light.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.11,0:10:04.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我父亲知道他来了吗？\N{\fs16}Does my father know he's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:06.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 不知道 - 好的\N{\fs16}- No. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:16.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,诸神慈悲\N{\fs16}Gods be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:17.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没事的 爵士\N{\fs16}It's all right, ser.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.51,0:11:13.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我带了个礼物给你\N{\fs16}I bought you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.60,0:11:19.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你知道这是什么吗？\N{\fs16}Do you know what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:22.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,瓦雷利亚钢\N{\fs16}It's Valyrian steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.06,0:11:25.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,和黑暗姐妹一样\N{\fs16}Like Dark Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.57,0:11:30.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,转过身去\N{\fs16}Turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.42,0:11:46.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在\N{\fs16}Now
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.88,0:11:51.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你和我都拥有了我们祖先的一小块物品\N{\fs16}you and I both own a small piece of our ancestry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:04.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 你看书了吗？ -  我当然看了\N{\fs16}- Did you read it? - Of course, I read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:06.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,娜梅莉亚公主到了多恩以后\N{\fs16}When Princess Nymeria arrived in Dorne
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:08.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,选择的丈夫是谁？\N{\fs16}who did she take to husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.77,0:12:10.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一个男的\N{\fs16}A man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.23,0:12:11.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他的名字是？\N{\fs16}What was his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.82,0:12:13.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,某某大人\N{\fs16}Lord Something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.03,0:12:17.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果你拿“某某大人”当答案 玛洛修女得气疯了\N{\fs16}If you answer with "Lord Something," Septa Marlow will be furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:19.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她生起气来可好玩了\N{\fs16}She's funny when she's furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:24.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你有心事的时候就是现在这样\N{\fs16}You're always like this when you're worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.91,0:12:26.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,哪样？\N{\fs16}Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:27.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不好相处\N{\fs16}Disagreeable.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.92,0:12:34.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你担心你父亲会因为有了儿子\N{\fs16}You're worried your father is about to overshadow you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:35.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而忽略你\N{\fs16}with a son.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:37.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我只是替我母亲担心\N{\fs16}I only worry for my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:40.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我希望父亲能有个儿子\N{\fs16}I hope for my father that he gets a son.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.85,0:12:44.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,从我记事开始 这就是他一直想要的\N{\fs16}As long as I can recall, it's all he's wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:46.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你希望他有儿子？\N{\fs16}You want him to have a son?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:49.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我希望能和你一起骑龙\N{\fs16}I want to fly with you on dragonback
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:50.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,飞越狭海 看看那边的奇观\N{\fs16}see the great wonders across the Narrow Sea
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:52.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还希望只吃蛋糕\N{\fs16}and eat only cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.36,0:12:54.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 我是认真的 - 我从不拿蛋糕开玩笑\N{\fs16}- I'm being serious. - I never jest about cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.28,0:12:57.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你不担心你的位置吗？\N{\fs16}You aren't worried about your position?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.20,0:13:00.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我喜欢现在的位置 非常舒服\N{\fs16}I like this position. It's quite comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:04.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你要去哪儿？\N{\fs16}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:07.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,回家 时间晚了\N{\fs16}Home. The hour has grown late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.25,0:13:12.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,娜梅莉亚公主带领洛伊拿人乘坐一万艘船横渡狭海\N{\fs16}Princess Nymeria led her Rhoynar across the Narrow Sea on 10,000 ships
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:14.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,以躲避瓦雷利亚人的追捕\N{\fs16}to flee their Valyrian pursuers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.59,0:13:17.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她选了多恩的莫尔斯·马泰尔作丈夫\N{\fs16}She took Lord Mors Martell of Dorne to husband
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.76,0:13:19.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在阳戟城下烧毁了她的整支舰队\N{\fs16}and burned her own fleet off Sunspear
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:22.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,以宣告她的子民从今以后无需逃亡\N{\fs16}to show her people that they were finished running.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.06,0:13:26.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 你在干嘛？ - 这样你才能记住\N{\fs16}- What are you doing? - So you remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.39,0:13:30.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 如果修女看到这本书 那…… - 去他妈的修女\N{\fs16}- If the Septa sees this book then... - Fuck the Septa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:31.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉！\N{\fs16}Rhaenyra!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.58,0:13:45.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在愈合了吗？\N{\fs16}Is it healing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.04,0:13:48.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,愈合得很慢 陛下\N{\fs16}It has grown slightly, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:53.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在知道这是什么了吗？\N{\fs16}Can you say yet what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.21,0:13:55.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们已经向学城发信询问\N{\fs16}We've sent inquiries to the Citadel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:57.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们正在书中查找相似的案例\N{\fs16}They are searching the texts for similar cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.76,0:14:00.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这只是被王座割开的细小伤口\N{\fs16}It's a small cut from sitting the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:01.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没什么大事\N{\fs16}It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.22,0:14:04.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王承受了巨大的压力\N{\fs16}The King has been under heavy stresses
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:06.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,因为要为新生儿作准备\N{\fs16}preparing for the birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.89,0:14:11.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不良的精神状态会对身体造成不好的影响\N{\fs16}Bad humors of the mind can adversely affect the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.56,0:14:14.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不论是什么事 都不要声张\N{\fs16}Whatever it is, it needs to be kept quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.28,0:14:19.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们应该再用水蛭放血 学士\N{\fs16}We should leech it again, maester.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:22.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这伤口无法愈合 大学士\N{\fs16}It's a wound that refuses to heal, Grand Maester.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:25.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我能否建议用烧灼疗法试试？\N{\fs16}Might I suggest cauterization?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:29.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,烧灼疗法也许是明智之举 陛下\N{\fs16}Cauterization would be a wise course of treatment, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:31.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 只是那会很疼…… - 好吧\N{\fs16}- It will be painful... - Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.42,0:14:34.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就这样\N{\fs16}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:49.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你泡在浴缸里的时间比我坐在铁王座上的时间还久\N{\fs16}You spend more time in that bath than I do on the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.98,0:14:54.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是这些天来唯一一处让我感到舒适的地方\N{\fs16}This is the only place I can find comfort these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.73,0:14:58.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,只有一点温\N{\fs16}It's tepid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:00.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,学士们不允许更烫\N{\fs16}It's as warm as the maesters will allow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.03,0:15:03.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们难道不知道龙喜欢热吗？\N{\fs16}Don't they know dragons prefer heat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:06.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,经历这次痛苦的孕期后\N{\fs16}After this miserable pregnancy
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.66,0:15:10.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我若生出一条真龙 都不觉得奇怪了\N{\fs16}I wouldn't be surprised if I hatched an actual dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:13.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那他会受到疼爱和珍视\N{\fs16}Then he will be loved and cherished.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.42,0:15:17.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉已经宣布自己会有个妹妹了\N{\fs16}Rhaenyra has already declared that she is to have a sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.46,0:15:18.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,真的么？\N{\fs16}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.05,0:15:22.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 她甚至为她取好了名字. - 我能问吗？\N{\fs16}- She even named her. - Dare I ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.88,0:15:24.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,维桑尼亚\N{\fs16}Visenya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:26.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她已经选好了放进摇篮的龙蛋\N{\fs16}She chose a dragon's egg for the cradle
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.35,0:15:28.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她说这枚蛋让她想起了瓦格哈尔\N{\fs16}that she said reminded her of Vhagar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.22,0:15:29.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,诸神慈悲\N{\fs16}Gods be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.77,0:15:32.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这个家庭已经有了个维桑尼亚\N{\fs16}This family already has its Visenya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:36.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有你亲爱的弟弟的消息吗？\N{\fs16}Has there been any word from your dear brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.98,0:15:39.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,自从任命他为都城守备队司令后就没个信了\N{\fs16}Not since I named him Commander of the City Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.44,0:15:42.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我相信他一定会出现在比武大会\N{\fs16}I'm sure he will reemerge for the tourney.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:46.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他向来无法拒绝亲自参赛\N{\fs16}He could never stay away from the lists.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:47.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,比武大会\N{\fs16}The tourney
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.62,0:15:50.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,为庆祝我们还未出世的长子而办\N{\fs16}to celebrate the firstborn son that we presently do not have.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.08,0:15:53.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你得明白\N{\fs16}You do understand
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:55.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果宝宝本身没有小鸡鸡\N{\fs16}nothing will cause the babe to grow a cock
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:15:57.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也没什么办法硬长出来吧？\N{\fs16}if it does not already possess one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.25,0:16:00.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是个男孩 爱玛\N{\fs16}This child is a boy, Aemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.88,0:16:02.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我很确定\N{\fs16}I'm certain of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:05.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我从来没有这么确定过\N{\fs16}I've never been more certain of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:10.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那个梦\N{\fs16}The dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:13.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,比记忆还清晰\N{\fs16}It was clearer than a memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:18.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们的儿子戴着伊耿的王冠降生\N{\fs16}Our son was born wearing Aegon's iron crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:23.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我听到雷鸣般的马蹄声\N{\fs16}When I heard the sound of thundering hooves
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:27.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,盾牌破碎和挥剑的声音\N{\fs16}splintering shields, and ringing swords
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:29.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我把我们的儿子放在铁王座上\N{\fs16}and I placed our son upon the Iron Throne
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:36.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,圣堂的钟声响起 所有巨龙齐声而吼\N{\fs16}as the bells of the Grand Sept tolled and all the dragons roared as one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.71,0:16:41.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴着王冠出生？\N{\fs16}Born wearing a crown?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.05,0:16:46.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,诸神救救我吧 生孩子已经很难受了\N{\fs16}Gods spare me, birth is unpleasant enough as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:58.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是最后一次了吗 韦赛里斯\N{\fs16}This is the last time, Viserys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:04.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我有个宝宝死于襁褓 生下过两个死胎\N{\fs16}I've lost one babe in the cradle, had two stillbirths
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:07.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还有两次怀孕在足月前就结束了\N{\fs16}and two pregnancies ended well before their term.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.41,0:17:13.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,五个孩子 前后耗费了十年\N{\fs16}That's five in twice as many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.79,0:17:17.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我知道 为你生下继承人是我的责任\N{\fs16}I know it is my duty to provide you an heir
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.87,0:17:20.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果为此让你失望了 我很抱歉\N{\fs16}and I'm sorry if I have failed you in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.42,0:17:21.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉\N{\fs16}I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.26,0:17:28.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但我没法再悼念更多死去的孩子了\N{\fs16}But I've mourned all the dead children I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:51.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,司令到场！\N{\fs16}Commander on the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:18:01.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当我接下都城守备队司令一职时 你们还是一群\N{\fs16}When I took command of the Watch, you were stray mongrels
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:05.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,饥饿散漫的野狗\N{\fs16}starving and undisciplined.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:10.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如今 你们成为了一队猎犬\N{\fs16}Now, you're a pack of hounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.93,0:18:13.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,酒足饭饱 历经磨练 随时可以狩猎\N{\fs16}You're sated and honed for the hunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.18,0:18:20.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我哥哥的城市已经变得堕落不堪\N{\fs16}My brother's city has fallen into squalor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:25.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,各种罪行肆意滋生 猖獗横行\N{\fs16}Crime of every breed has been allowed to thrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.03,0:18:28.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这种日子到头了\N{\fs16}No longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.49,0:18:29.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,从今晚起\N{\fs16}Beginning tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.61,0:18:32.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,君临将学会畏惧金色\N{\fs16}King's Landing will learn to fear the color gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.91,0:19:20.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,起身！\N{\fs16}Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.14,0:19:41.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,强奸犯！\N{\fs16}Raper!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.52,0:19:46.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不！不要……不！\N{\fs16}No! No... no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.36,0:19:55.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,小偷！\N{\fs16}Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.24,0:19:57.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不！\N{\fs16}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.41,0:20:04.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,杀人犯！\N{\fs16}Murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.26,0:20:24.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是一次对各类犯罪的空前围捕\N{\fs16}It was an unprecedented roundup of criminals of every ilk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:26.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你弟弟当众做秀\N{\fs16}Your brother made a public show of it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.56,0:20:29.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,亲自做出裁决\N{\fs16}meting out the summary judgments himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:31.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我听说他们得用双驾马车\N{\fs16}I'm told they needed a two-horse cart
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:36.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,才拉走了所有被肢解的人体\N{\fs16}to haul away the resulting dismemberments when it was done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:38.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,诸神慈悲\N{\fs16}Gods be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.74,0:20:43.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不能让王子如此肆无忌惮 还逍遥法外\N{\fs16}The Prince cannot be allowed to act with this kind of unchecked impunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:47.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 哥哥 - 戴蒙\N{\fs16}- Brother. - Daemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:20:52.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,继续啊 你刚正说我逍遥法外的事\N{\fs16}Carry on. You were saying something about my impunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.88,0:20:58.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你需要解释一下你带领都城守备队的所作所为\N{\fs16}You are to explain your doings with the City Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:02.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你新组的金袍子\N{\fs16}Your new gold cloaks
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:04.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,昨晚干了一番大事  不是吗？\N{\fs16}made quite the impression last night, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.27,0:21:05.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是吗？\N{\fs16}Did they?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.39,0:21:08.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,都城守备队可不是你想挥就挥的剑\N{\fs16}The City Watch is not a sword to be wielded at your whim.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.69,0:21:10.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们是国王权力的延伸\N{\fs16}They're an extension of the crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.73,0:21:12.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,都城守备等同于执行着国王的法律\N{\fs16}The Watch was enforcing the crown's laws.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.77,0:21:14.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你不同意吗 斯壮大人？\N{\fs16}Wouldn't you agree, Lord Strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.69,0:21:17.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王子殿下 我不认为……\N{\fs16}My Prince, I don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.15,0:21:19.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在公众面前肆意展示暴行\N{\fs16}Making a public spectacle of wanton brutality
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.82,0:21:21.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,与我们的法律毫无关系\N{\fs16}is hardly in line with our laws.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.70,0:21:23.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,全境各地的贵族\N{\fs16}Nobles from every corner of the realm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.45,0:21:25.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而今都将聚集在君临\N{\fs16}are right now descending upon King's Landing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.50,0:21:26.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,来参加我哥哥的比武大会\N{\fs16}for my brother's tourney.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.96,0:21:29.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你难道想这些贵族被抢劫 被强暴 被谋杀吗？\N{\fs16}Do you want them mugged, raped, murdered?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.67,0:21:32.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,除非你离开红堡的安全地带 才会知道这些\N{\fs16}You mightn't know this unless you left the safety of the Red Keep
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.59,0:21:35.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,君临的大部分地区 在老百姓眼里都是\N{\fs16}but much of King's Landing is seen by the smallfolk
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.09,0:21:37.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,无法无天的可怕去处\N{\fs16}as lawless and terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.14,0:21:42.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们的城市应该让所有人感到安全\N{\fs16}Our city should be safe for all its people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.22,0:21:44.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我同意\N{\fs16}I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.06,0:21:48.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我只是希望你不要把我的都城中一半的人弄残就能实现这点\N{\fs16}I just hope you don't have to maim half of my city to achieve this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.27,0:21:50.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,时间会证明一切\N{\fs16}Time will tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.11,0:21:55.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们任命戴蒙王子为司令\N{\fs16}We installed Prince Daemon as commander
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.32,0:21:57.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,来改善法律和秩序\N{\fs16}to promote law and order.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.24,0:21:59.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,犯罪分子理当惧怕都城守备队\N{\fs16}The criminal element should fear the City Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.78,0:22:01.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的支持 科利斯伯爵\N{\fs16}Thank you for your support, Lord Corlys.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.57,0:22:03.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,倘若王子能对他的夫人\N{\fs16}If only the Prince would show the same devotion
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.37,0:22:06.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,像对工作一样热情就好了 陛下\N{\fs16}to his lady wife as he does his work, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:10.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你很久没有去谷地或符石城了\N{\fs16}You've not been seen in the Vale or at Runestone for quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.25,0:22:12.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不去那边 我的青铜婊子可能更开心些\N{\fs16}I think my bronze bitch is happier for my absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.63,0:22:14.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷娅夫人是你的妻子\N{\fs16}Lady Rhea is your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.42,0:22:16.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一位善良可敬的谷地女士\N{\fs16}A good and honorable lady of the Vale.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.55,0:22:19.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在谷地 听说男人操羊而不是女人\N{\fs16}In the Vale, men are said to fuck sheep instead of women.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.55,0:22:21.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我敢向你保证 羊美多了\N{\fs16}I can assure you, the sheep are prettier.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.97,0:22:23.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\fs16}Dear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.09,0:22:25.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你在七神面前发过誓 在婚姻中会尊重你的妻子\N{\fs16}You made a vow before the Seven to honor your wife in marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.93,0:22:28.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那么我很乐意将雷娅夫人送给你 海塔尔伯爵\N{\fs16}Well, I'd gladly give Lady Rhea to you, Lord Hightower
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.60,0:22:31.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果你需要女人暖床的话\N{\fs16}if you're in want of a woman to warm your bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.56,0:22:34.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你的妻子刚好最近过世\N{\fs16}Your own lady wife passed recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.40,0:22:37.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不是吗？\N{\fs16}Did she not?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.19,0:22:39.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,奥托\N{\fs16}Otto.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.57,0:22:44.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,也许你还没从悲伤中走出来\N{\fs16}Perhaps you aren't ready to move on just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.87,0:22:48.70,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你知道我弟弟总喜欢刺激你\N{\fs16}You know how my brother makes sport of provoking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:50.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你非得上当吗？\N{\fs16}Must you indulge him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.92,0:22:56.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的错 陛下\N{\fs16}My apologies, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.00,0:22:59.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,御前会议可是花了大价钱\N{\fs16}This council has, at great expense
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.96,0:23:02.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,才将都城守备队改善到你要求的标准\N{\fs16}bettered the City Watch to your exacting standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.01,0:23:05.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,执行我的法律 但要明白\N{\fs16}Enforce my laws, but understand
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.05,0:23:09.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果再有昨晚那样的行动 将会受到惩罚\N{\fs16}any further performances like last night's will be answered.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.65,0:23:15.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,知道了 陛下\N{\fs16}Understood, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.95,0:23:31.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我祖母去世后 君临治安每况愈下\N{\fs16}King's Landing has been in decline since my grandmother passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.58,0:23:34.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,到头来\N{\fs16}In the end
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.67,0:23:37.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这个新的都城守备队可能是个好事\N{\fs16}this new City Watch might be a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.09,0:24:26.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是什么惹你心烦 我的王子？\N{\fs16}What troubles you, my Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.52,0:24:34.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我可以再叫来一个人\N{\fs16}I could bring in another.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.10,0:24:36.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,或者找个处女\N{\fs16}Perhaps a maiden.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.77,0:24:39.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我有好几个\N{\fs16}I have several.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.19,0:24:43.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,甚至可以安排个银发姑娘\N{\fs16}I could even arrange one with silver hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.24,0:24:52.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你是戴蒙·坦格利安\N{\fs16}You are Daemon Targaryen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.04,0:24:56.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,科拉克休的骑手 暗黑姐妹的持有者\N{\fs16}Rider of Caraxes. Wielder of Dark Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.96,0:24:59.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王无法找人取代你\N{\fs16}The King cannot replace you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.10,0:25:13.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,欢迎！\N{\fs16}Be welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.64,0:25:17.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我知道你们很多人为了参加这次比武大会\N{\fs16}I know many of you have traveled long leagues
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.23,0:25:18.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,都远道而来\N{\fs16}to be at these games
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.40,0:25:22.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但我保证 你们不会失望的\N{\fs16}but I promise, you will not be disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.03,0:25:27.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当我看着名单中这些优秀的骑士时\N{\fs16}When I look at the fine knights in these lists
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.24,0:25:30.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我看到了一群无可匹敌的勇士\N{\fs16}I see a group without equal in our histories.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.16,0:25:37.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而且这个伟大的日子还有更多吉兆\N{\fs16}And this great day has been made more auspicious
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.41,0:25:41.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我很开心地宣布这个消息\N{\fs16}by the news that I am happy to share.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.21,0:25:45.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,爱玛王后已经开始分娩了！\N{\fs16}Queen Aemma has begun her labors!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.72,0:25:52.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,愿七神的好运降临在所有参赛者身上！\N{\fs16}May the luck of the Seven shine upon all combatants!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.75,0:26:26.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一个神秘骑士？\N{\fs16}A mystery knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.05,0:26:29.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不 科尔家的人 来自风暴地\N{\fs16}No, a Cole, of the Stormlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.38,0:26:30.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我从没听说过科尔家族\N{\fs16}I've never heard of House Cole.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.72,0:26:33.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮丝·坦格利安公主！\N{\fs16}Princess Rhaenys Targaryen!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.55,0:26:37.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我在此恭请无冕女王的信物\N{\fs16}I would humbly ask for the favor of The Queen Who Never Was.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.15,0:26:45.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,祝你好运 老表\N{\fs16}Good fortune to you, cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.77,0:26:48.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果我需要好运的话 会乐意接受它的\N{\fs16}I would gladly take it if I thought I needed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.62,0:26:57.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就冲这番话 你可以把拜拉席恩的舌头割下来\N{\fs16}You could have Baratheon's tongue for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.83,0:26:59.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,舌头又不会改变继承人\N{\fs16}Tongues will not change the succession.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.20,0:27:01.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,随他去吧\N{\fs16}Let them wag.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.09,0:27:09.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,史铎克渥斯伯爵的女儿\N{\fs16}Lord Stokeworth's daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.76,0:27:11.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,已经被许给了那个塔利家的年轻侍从\N{\fs16}is promised to that young Tarly squire.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.42,0:27:13.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,马赛伯爵的儿子？\N{\fs16}Lord Massey's son?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.22,0:27:15.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,等他获得骑士头衔 便会完婚\N{\fs16}They're to be married as soon as he wins his knighthood.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.14,0:27:17.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,最好快点\N{\fs16}Best get on with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.64,0:27:19.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我听说埃萝小姐\N{\fs16}I heard that Lady Elinor
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.89,0:27:22.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,努力藏着裙子下面隆起的肚子\N{\fs16}is hiding a swollen belly beneath her dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.04,0:27:47.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你对克里斯顿·科尔爵士了解多少 哈罗德爵士？\N{\fs16}What do you know about this Ser Criston Cole, Ser Harrold?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.50,0:27:51.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我听说克里斯顿爵士出身平民 是唐德利恩伯爵管家的儿子\N{\fs16}I'm told Ser Criston is common-born, son of Lord Dondarrion's steward.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.13,0:27:54.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,除了这个 以及他刚刚把\N{\fs16}But other than that, and the fact that he's just unhorsed
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.09,0:27:57.72,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,拜拉席恩家的两个孩子打下马的事实 我就不知道了\N{\fs16}both of the Baratheon lads, I really couldn't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.41,0:28:19.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,坦格利安家族的戴蒙王子\N{\fs16}Prince Daemon of House Targaryen!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.83,0:28:25.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,首都亲王即将选择他的第一位对手\N{\fs16}Prince of the City will now choose his first opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.74,0:29:07.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙·坦格利安的第一位对手是——\N{\fs16}For his first challenge, Prince Daemon Targaryen chooses
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.17,0:29:13.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,旧镇的加尔温·海塔尔爵士 首相的长子\N{\fs16}Ser Gwayne Hightower of Oldtown, eldest son of the Hand of the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.14,0:29:28.90,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,五金龙押戴蒙\N{\fs16}Five dragons on Daemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.80,0:30:44.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 干得漂亮 叔叔 - 谢谢你 公主\N{\fs16}- Nicely done, Uncle. - Thank you, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.89,0:30:49.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我敢说 我胜券在握 阿莉森小姐\N{\fs16}Now, I'm fairly certain I can win these games, Lady Alicent.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.81,0:30:53.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,得到你的信物会让我如虎添翼\N{\fs16}Having your favor would all but assure it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.29,0:31:08.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,祝你好运 王子\N{\fs16}Good luck, my Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.26,0:31:30.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,用力！\N{\fs16}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.86,0:31:37.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,怎么回事？\N{\fs16}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.02,0:31:39.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下 胎儿是臀位\N{\fs16}The infant is in breech, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.65,0:31:42.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,所有扶正胎位的尝试都失败了\N{\fs16}All attempts to turn the babe have failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.41,0:31:45.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,别干看着啊！\N{\fs16}Do something for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.57,0:31:47.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们已经给了她很多罂粟花奶\N{\fs16}We've given her as much milk of the poppy as we can
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.70,0:31:49.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,再加量孩子就有危险\N{\fs16}without risking the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.29,0:31:50.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王后是位坚强的女性\N{\fs16}Your Queen is a strong woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.04,0:31:54.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她已经拼劲全力了 但恐怕还是不行\N{\fs16}She's fighting with all her might, but it may not be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.58,0:31:56.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不！\N{\fs16}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.13,0:31:57.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,艾玛\N{\fs16}Aemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.92,0:32:00.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,艾玛 我在的\N{\fs16}Aemma, I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.96,0:32:02.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我在\N{\fs16}I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.47,0:32:05.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有我在 没事的\N{\fs16}I'm here. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.55,0:32:07.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 没事的 - 我不想继续了\N{\fs16}- It's all right. - I don't wanna do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.97,0:32:09.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你不会有事的\N{\fs16}You're going to be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.89,0:32:11.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不会有事的\N{\fs16}You're going to be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.79,0:32:12.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,抓住我的手\N{\fs16}Hold my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.62,0:32:37.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,杀了他！\N{\fs16}Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.83,0:32:40.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,真是越来越难看了\N{\fs16}And the day grows ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.67,0:32:46.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,真不知是否应该用这样的方式\N{\fs16}I wonder if this is how we should celebrate
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.09,0:32:48.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,来庆祝王储的诞生\N{\fs16}the birth of our future king.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.80,0:32:50.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如此挥霍暴力\N{\fs16}With wanton violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.26,0:32:52.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,梅葛国王死后 已经过了七十年\N{\fs16}It's been 70 years since King Maegor's end.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.64,0:32:54.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这群骑士都嫩得像夏天的青草\N{\fs16}These knights are as green as summer grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.48,0:32:56.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们都没见识过真正的战争\N{\fs16}None have known real war.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.40,0:32:58.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,封君把他们送到比武场上\N{\fs16}Their lords sent them to the tourney field
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.06,0:33:01.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,手中握剑精力充沛 胯下宝剑也是干劲十足\N{\fs16}with fists full of steel and balls full of seed
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.02,0:33:04.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而我们还指望他们表现得荣誉而优雅\N{\fs16}and we expect them to act with honor and grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.74,0:33:07.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这一滴血没引发战争就已经是奇迹了\N{\fs16}It's a marvel that war didn't break out at first blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.30,0:33:31.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,梅罗斯？\N{\fs16}Mellos?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.35,0:33:33.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下\N{\fs16}Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.02,0:33:36.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,请来一下\N{\fs16}If you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.36,0:33:48.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,难产的时候\N{\fs16}During a difficult birth
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.11,0:33:52.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,父亲有时候不得不\N{\fs16}it sometimes becomes necessary for the father
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.33,0:33:55.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,做出艰难抉择\N{\fs16}to make an impossible choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.62,0:33:58.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,说吧\N{\fs16}Well, speak it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.41,0:34:02.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是牺牲一个 还是一尸两命\N{\fs16}To sacrifice one or to lose them both.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.13,0:34:07.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有保住孩子的可能\N{\fs16}There is a chance that we can save the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.34,0:34:09.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,学城教授过一件技艺\N{\fs16}A technique is taught at the Citadel
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.43,0:34:11.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,可以直接剖开子宫\N{\fs16}which involves cutting directly into the womb
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.51,0:34:13.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,取出婴儿\N{\fs16}to free the infant.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.39,0:34:16.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 但伴随的失血…… - 七层地狱 梅罗斯\N{\fs16}- But the resulting blood loss... - Seven Hells, Mellos.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.74,0:34:30.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你能保住孩子？\N{\fs16}You can save the child?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.95,0:34:35.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,必须立刻行动 否则就只能托付诸神了\N{\fs16}We must either act now or leave it with the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.71,0:34:49.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,克里斯顿·科尔爵士的长枪比武对手\N{\fs16}Ser Criston Cole will now tilt
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.34,0:34:53.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是戴蒙·坦格利安 首都亲王！\N{\fs16}against Ser Daemon Targaryen, Prince of the City!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.34,0:35:47.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,枪！\N{\fs16}Lance!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.29,0:36:07.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 韦赛里斯 - 我在\N{\fs16}- Viserys. - Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.38,0:36:11.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们现在要把孩子取出来了\N{\fs16}They're going to bring the babe out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.20,0:36:36.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我爱你\N{\fs16}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.58,0:36:46.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 怎么了？ - 没事的\N{\fs16}- What is happening? - No, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.92,0:36:49.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不要 怎么了？\N{\fs16}No, what is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.54,0:36:52.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 韦赛里斯 怎么…… - 没事的\N{\fs16}- Viserys, what... - No, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.17,0:36:54.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 你们要干什么？ - 他们要把孩子取出来\N{\fs16}- What are you doing? - They're going to bring the babe out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.26,0:36:55.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们怎么……\N{\fs16}How are they...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.55,0:36:57.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 没事的 - 韦赛里斯 求你了\N{\fs16}- It's all right. - Viserys, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.18,0:36:59.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 没事的 - 不 我害怕\N{\fs16}- It's all right. - No, I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.51,0:37:00.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 别怕 - 怎么回事啊？\N{\fs16}- Don't be scared. - What is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.06,0:37:02.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,别害怕 他们要取出孩子\N{\fs16}Don't be scared. They're going to bring the babe out.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.77,0:37:05.43,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 哦不 - 没事的\N{\fs16}- Oh no. - It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.52,0:37:07.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们要取出孩子\N{\fs16}They're going to bring the babe out.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.81,0:37:11.27,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不 不要！\N{\fs16}No... no!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.36,0:37:13.53,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我要在这里切第一刀\N{\fs16}I'm making the first incision.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.61,0:37:16.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不 不！\N{\fs16}No... no!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.15,0:37:19.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,韦赛里斯 别这样！求你了！\N{\fs16}Viserys, no! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.16,0:37:21.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 不……不要！ - 别怕\N{\fs16}- No... no! - Don't be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.31,0:37:46.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,剑！\N{\fs16}Sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.85,0:37:48.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙·坦格利安王子\N{\fs16}Prince Daemon Targaryen
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.31,0:37:51.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,希望继续徒步比武！\N{\fs16}wishes to continue in a contest of arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.01,0:39:43.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,投降吧\N{\fs16}Yield.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.97,0:39:46.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,投降\N{\fs16}Yield.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.84,0:40:22.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,诸神啊！他是多恩人\N{\fs16}Gods. He's Dornish.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.30,0:40:24.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我希望得到公主的信物\N{\fs16}I was hoping to ask for the Princess's favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.98,0:40:39.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,祝你好运 克里斯顿爵士\N{\fs16}I wish you luck, Ser Criston.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.65,0:40:41.11,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,公主\N{\fs16}Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.37,0:40:54.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,祝贺您 陛下\N{\fs16}Congratulations, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.29,0:40:56.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您有儿子了\N{\fs16}You have a son.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.79,0:41:02.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是男孩？\N{\fs16}It's a boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.21,0:41:04.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,新的继承人 陛下\N{\fs16}A new heir, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.39,0:41:12.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您和王后起好名字了吗？\N{\fs16}Had you and the Queen chosen a name?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.39,0:41:17.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,贝尔隆\N{\fs16}Baelon.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.60,0:42:37.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们都在等你\N{\fs16}They're waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.32,0:43:34.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙焰\N{\fs16}Dracarys.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.95,0:44:15.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 雷妮拉呢？- 陛下\N{\fs16}- Where's Rhaenyra? - Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.57,0:44:18.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在这黑暗的时刻 我们极其不愿讨论这件事\N{\fs16}This is the last thing any of us wish to discuss
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.58,0:44:21.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但我认为事关紧要\N{\fs16}at this dark hour, but I consider the matter urgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.87,0:44:23.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,什么事？\N{\fs16}What matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.29,0:44:26.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,继承人的事\N{\fs16}That of your succession.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.50,0:44:28.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,刚发生的两件悲剧\N{\fs16}These recent tragedies
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.29,0:44:30.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,使您失去了明确的继承人\N{\fs16}have left you without an obvious heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.21,0:44:31.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王有继承人 首相大人\N{\fs16}The King has an heir, my Lord Hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.88,0:44:34.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,尽管现在是难受的时候 陛下\N{\fs16}Despite how difficult this time is, Your Grace
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.63,0:44:37.68,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我认为极有必要确定继承人\N{\fs16}I feel it important the succession be firmly in place
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.76,0:44:39.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,以维护王国的稳定\N{\fs16}for the stability of the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.26,0:44:43.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,继承人早已根据惯例和律法选定\N{\fs16}The succession is already set by precedent and by law.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.14,0:44:44.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不妨说出他的名字？\N{\fs16}Shall we say his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.27,0:44:48.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙·坦格利安\N{\fs16}Daemon Targaryen.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.90,0:44:51.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果依然让戴蒙作为无可争议的继承人\N{\fs16}If Daemon were to remain the uncontested heir
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.94,0:44:54.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,可能带来王国的动荡\N{\fs16}it could destabilize the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.49,0:44:56.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王国？还是御前会议？\N{\fs16}The realm? Or this council?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.53,0:44:59.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在座诸位谁都不知道戴蒙会成为什么样的国王\N{\fs16}No one here can know what Daemon would do were he king
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.37,0:45:02.16,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但没人会怀疑他的野心\N{\fs16}but no one can doubt his ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.24,0:45:04.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,看看他用金袍子干了什么\N{\fs16}Look at what he did with the gold cloaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.83,0:45:06.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,都城守备队对他忠心耿耿\N{\fs16}The City Watch is fiercely loyal to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.96,0:45:10.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 一支两千人的军队 - 一支你给他的军队 奥托\N{\fs16}- An army 2,000 strong. - An army you gave him, Otto.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.79,0:45:14.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我任命戴蒙为法务大臣 你说他是个暴君\N{\fs16}I named Daemon Master of Laws, but you said he was a tyrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.88,0:45:15.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,任命他为财政大臣\N{\fs16}As Master of Coin
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.01,0:45:18.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你说他挥霍无度 会让国家破产\N{\fs16}you said he was a spendthrift that would beggar the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.01,0:45:22.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让戴蒙去领导都城守备队正是你的解决之道！\N{\fs16}Putting Daemon in command of the City Watch was your solution!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.93,0:45:24.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是权宜之计 陛下\N{\fs16}A half-measure, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.02,0:45:27.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,事实是 戴蒙应该远离宫廷\N{\fs16}The truth is, Daemon should be far away from this court.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.02,0:45:30.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙是我的弟弟\N{\fs16}Daemon is my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.11,0:45:31.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的血亲\N{\fs16}My blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.40,0:45:34.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他会在我的宫中有一席之地\N{\fs16}And he will have his place at my court.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.44,0:45:36.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那就给他在宫中留下一席之地吧 陛下\N{\fs16}Let him keep his place at court, Your Grace
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.74,0:45:40.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但如果七神将更多悲剧降临到您身上\N{\fs16}but if the gods should visit some further tragedy on you
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.91,0:45:43.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 有意无意之间…… - “有意”？\N{\fs16}- either by design or accident... - "Design"?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.54,0:45:45.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你是什么意思？\N{\fs16}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.04,0:45:48.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我弟弟会杀死我 夺走王位？\N{\fs16}My brother would murder me, take my crown?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.04,0:45:51.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是吗？\N{\fs16}Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.92,0:45:54.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,拜托\N{\fs16}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.09,0:45:58.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙是有野心 没错 但不是觊觎铁王座\N{\fs16}Daemon has ambition, yes, but not for the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.80,0:46:00.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他对这事没有耐心\N{\fs16}He lacks the patience for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.64,0:46:02.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,诸神还没有创造出\N{\fs16}The gods have yet to make a man
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.43,0:46:05.89,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一个对绝对权力没有耐心的人呢 陛下\N{\fs16}who lacks the patience for absolute power, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.97,0:46:09.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,在这种情况下 国王指定一个继承人\N{\fs16}Under such circumstances, it would not be an aberration
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.94,0:46:12.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,倒也不算脱离常规\N{\fs16}for the King to name a successor.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.40,0:46:14.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那么 还有谁有资格呢？\N{\fs16}Well, who else would have a claim?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.99,0:46:23.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王的第一个孩子\N{\fs16}The King's firstborn child.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.16,0:46:25.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉？一个女孩？\N{\fs16}Rhaenyra? A girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.08,0:46:29.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,铁王座上从没坐过女王\N{\fs16}No queen has ever sat the Iron Throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.16,0:46:31.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这只是依据传统和先例罢了 斯壮大人\N{\fs16}That is only by tradition and precedent, Lord Strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.29,0:46:33.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果御前会议这么关心秩序和稳定\N{\fs16}If order and stability so concerns this council
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.63,0:46:35.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那么我们或许不应该打破百年来的传统\N{\fs16}then perhaps we shouldn't break 100 years of it
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.71,0:46:37.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让一个女孩成为王嗣\N{\fs16}by naming a girl heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.55,0:46:41.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙会成为第二个梅葛 甚至更糟\N{\fs16}Daemon would be a second Maegor, or worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.34,0:46:43.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他冲动而又暴力\N{\fs16}He is impulsive and violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.05,0:46:45.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,保护国王和他的王国不受戴蒙侵害\N{\fs16}It is the duty of this council
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.01,0:46:49.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,正是我们这个御前会议的责任\N{\fs16}to protect the King and the realm from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.44,0:46:52.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,抱歉 陛下 但这恐怕不是我所看到的真相\N{\fs16}I'm sorry, Your Grace, but that is the truth as I see it
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.02,0:46:54.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而且我知道这里有人跟我想法一致\N{\fs16}and I know that others here agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.52,0:46:58.49,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我是不会被迫在我的兄弟和女儿之间做出选择的\N{\fs16}I will not be made to choose between my brother and my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.57,0:47:00.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,您不必如此 陛下\N{\fs16}You wouldn't have to, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.45,0:47:02.86,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,还有其他人选\N{\fs16}There are others who would have a claim.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.95,0:47:04.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,比如你的夫人？科利斯大人\N{\fs16}Such as your wife, Lord Corlys?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.66,0:47:05.80,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,无冕女王？\N{\fs16}The Queen Who Never Was?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.80,0:47:08.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮丝是杰赫里斯一世长子的独女\N{\fs16}Rhaenys was the only child of Jaehaerys' eldest son.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.33,0:47:10.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她在大议会时拥有很强的继承权主张\N{\fs16}She had a strong claim at the Great Council
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.41,0:47:11.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而且她已经有了一位男性继承人\N{\fs16}and she already has a male heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.75,0:47:15.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就在刚刚 你才声明支持戴蒙\N{\fs16}Just moments ago, you announced your support for Daemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.13,0:47:16.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果我们都不能在继承人问题上取得一致 那还怎么指望……\N{\fs16}If we cannot agree on an heir, then how can we expect……
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.75,0:47:18.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的妻儿都死了!\N{\fs16}My wife and son are dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.63,0:47:25.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不要再坐在这里忍受你们这群享用遗体的乌鸦!\N{\fs16}I will not sit here and suffer crows that come to feast on their corpses!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.09,0:48:02.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,派只渡鸦到旧镇去 马上\N{\fs16}Send a raven to Oldtown. Straight away.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.18,0:48:06.55,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,小姐\N{\fs16}My Lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.94,0:48:18.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,亲爱的\N{\fs16}My darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.53,0:48:29.20,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉怎么样了？\N{\fs16}How's Rhaenyra?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.91,0:48:33.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,她失去了母亲\N{\fs16}She lost her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.21,0:48:37.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,王后一直受所有人爱戴\N{\fs16}The Queen has been well-loved by all.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.71,0:48:42.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,今天我也想起了你的母亲\N{\fs16}I found myself thinking of your own mother today.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.51,0:48:51.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 陛下怎么样了？- 非常低落\N{\fs16}- How is His Grace? - Very low.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.64,0:48:55.39,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,所以我叫你来\N{\fs16}Which is why I sent for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.77,0:49:04.99,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我认为你该去找他 安慰他\N{\fs16}I thought you might go to him, offer him comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.61,0:49:08.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,去他房间？\N{\fs16}In his chambers?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.62,0:49:17.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不知道该说些什么\N{\fs16}I wouldn't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.04,0:49:19.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,别咬了\N{\fs16}Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.13,0:49:23.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他会很开心有人去看他\N{\fs16}He'll be glad of a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.47,0:49:33.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,可以穿条你母亲的裙子\N{\fs16}You might wear one of your mother's dresses.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.51,0:50:13.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下 阿莉森·海塔尔小姐求见\N{\fs16}The Lady Alicent Hightower, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.85,0:50:20.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,什么事 阿莉森？\N{\fs16}What is it, Alicent?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.06,0:50:23.36,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我觉得该来看看您 陛下\N{\fs16}I thought I might come and look in on you, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.19,0:50:26.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我带来了一本书\N{\fs16}I brought a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.03,0:50:30.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,真体贴 谢谢你\N{\fs16}That's very kind, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.99,0:50:37.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是我最爱的一本书\N{\fs16}It's a favorite of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.29,0:50:40.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我知道您有多热衷历史\N{\fs16}I do know how passionate you are for the histories.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.17,0:50:44.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs16}Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.81,0:51:03.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我母亲离世的时候\N{\fs16}When my mother died
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.94,0:51:07.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,人们只会拐弯抹角地和我说话\N{\fs16}people only ever spoke to me in riddles.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.19,0:51:11.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而我想要的 只是有人能对我的遭遇\N{\fs16}All I wanted was for someone to say that they were sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.32,0:51:13.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,表示难过\N{\fs16}for what happened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.12,0:51:18.95,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我很难过 陛下\N{\fs16}I'm very sorry, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.00,0:52:08.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs16}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.05,0:52:12.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,再次成为国王的唯一继承人\N{\fs16}The King's sole heir once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.26,0:52:17.47,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,不为我们的未来干一杯吗？\N{\fs16}Might we drink to our future?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.72,0:52:20.22,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,安静！\N{\fs16}Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.31,0:52:23.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,让王子来说几句！\N{\fs16}Your Prince will speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.40,0:52:28.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,安静！\N{\fs16}Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.95,0:52:36.03,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,陛下 在我们开始会议之前\N{\fs16}Before we begin, Your Grace
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.11,0:52:40.45,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,有必要分享我收到的一封密报\N{\fs16}I have a report I feel compelled to share.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.16,0:52:43.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,昨晚\N{\fs16}Last night
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.29,0:52:47.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙王子买断了丝绸街上的\N{\fs16}Prince Daemon bought out one of the pleasure houses
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.13,0:52:48.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一家青楼\N{\fs16}on the Street of Silk
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.67,0:52:52.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,来款待都城守备队的士官\N{\fs16}to entertain officers of the City Watch
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.96,0:52:54.84,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,以及他的一些朋友\N{\fs16}and other friends of his.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.26,0:53:00.51,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,国王和御前会议一直对我王位继承人的身份\N{\fs16}King and Council have long rued my position
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.60,0:53:02.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,心生芥蒂\N{\fs16}as next in line for the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.02,0:53:09.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但随便他们怎么做梦和祈祷 我的位置看来不那么容易被取代\N{\fs16}But dream and pray as they all might, it seems I'm not so easily replaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.86,0:53:14.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,诸神一手给予 一手剥夺\N{\fs16}The gods give just as the gods take away.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.69,0:53:16.65,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他为贝尔隆王子举杯\N{\fs16}He toasted Prince Baelon.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.74,0:53:18.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,敬国王之子\N{\fs16}To the King's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.91,0:53:20.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,称他为……\N{\fs16}Styling him...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.66,0:53:24.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一日王储\N{\fs16}the Heir for a Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.04,0:53:35.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我和三名不同的证人确认了这份密报\N{\fs16}I corroborated this report with three separate witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.22,0:53:39.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,所有证据都表明 那晚是一场庆祝活动\N{\fs16}The evening was, by all accounts, a celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.43,0:53:44.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,哥哥 你真是一副征服者的派头\N{\fs16}You cut the image of the Conqueror, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.85,0:53:47.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你说过吗？\N{\fs16}Did you say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.44,0:53:50.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我不知道你指什么\N{\fs16}I don't know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.06,0:53:52.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你该称呼我为“陛下”\N{\fs16}You will address me as "Your Grace"
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.65,0:53:55.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,否则我会让御林铁卫割下你的舌头\N{\fs16}or I will have my Kingsguard cut out your tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.28,0:54:03.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,“一日王储” 你说过吗？\N{\fs16}"The Heir for a Day." Did you say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.13,0:54:16.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们都用自己的方式哀悼 陛下\N{\fs16}We must all mourn in our own way, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.59,0:54:20.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我的家庭刚毁了\N{\fs16}My family has just been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.05,0:54:25.06,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你却没待在我身边 或者雷妮拉身边\N{\fs16}But instead of being by my side, or Rhaenyra's
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.14,0:54:27.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而是选择去庆祝自己的晋升！\N{\fs16}you chose to celebrate your own rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.02,0:54:31.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,跟你的婊子和马屁精一起寻欢作乐！\N{\fs16}Laughing with your whores and your lickspittles!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.40,0:54:36.48,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你在宫廷之上除了我没有其他盟友！\N{\fs16}You have no allies at court but me!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.57,0:54:39.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我一直在维护你！\N{\fs16}I have only ever defended you!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.36,0:54:41.82,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,然而我给你的一切 你都弃之如敝屣扔回给了我\N{\fs16}Yet everything I've given you, you've thrown back in my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.91,0:54:43.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你只想把我赶走\N{\fs16}You've only ever tried to send me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.99,0:54:48.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,去谷地 去都城守备队 去那些远离你的地方\N{\fs16}To the Vale, to the City Watch, anywhere but by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.66,0:54:50.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你已经当了十年国王\N{\fs16}Ten years you've been king
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.75,0:54:53.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但你从未要求我做你的国王之手！\N{\fs16}and yet not once have you asked me to be your Hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.96,0:54:57.05,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 我为什么要那么做？ - 因为我是你的弟弟\N{\fs16}- Why would I do that? - Because I'm your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.21,0:55:00.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙血浓于水\N{\fs16}And the blood of the dragon runs thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.09,0:55:02.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那你为什么要伤我这么深？\N{\fs16}Then why do you cut me so deeply?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.34,0:55:06.26,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我说的只是真相 我看得出奥托·海塔尔的本来面目\N{\fs16}I've only ever spoken the truth. I see Otto Hightower for what he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.35,0:55:09.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 一位忠贞不移的国王之手？ - 一个婊子\N{\fs16}- An unwavering and loyal Hand? - A cunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.35,0:55:12.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一个次子 没法继承任何东西\N{\fs16}A second son who stands to inherit nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.52,0:55:13.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,除非自己争取\N{\fs16}he doesn't seize for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.90,0:55:16.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,奥托·海塔尔是一个值得尊敬的人\N{\fs16}Otto Hightower is a more honorable man
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.23,0:55:18.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 你这辈子也赶不上 - 他没有保护你\N{\fs16}- than you could ever be. - He doesn't protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.36,0:55:20.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 而我可以 - 从谁手中保护？\N{\fs16}- I would. - From what?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.28,0:55:21.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你自己\N{\fs16}Yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.20,0:55:27.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你是个懦弱的人 韦赛里斯\N{\fs16}You're weak, Viserys.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.62,0:55:32.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那些御前会议的水蛭都知道这一点\N{\fs16}And that council of leeches knows it.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.17,0:55:34.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们都为了自己的利益寄生在你身上\N{\fs16}They all prey on you for their own ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.09,0:55:41.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我已决定任命一位新的继承人\N{\fs16}I have decided to name a new heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.47,0:55:44.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 我就是你的继承人 - 不再是了\N{\fs16}- I'm your heir. - Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.26,0:55:48.85,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你要即刻回到符石城 回到你夫人身边\N{\fs16}You are to return to Runestone and your lady wife at once
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.93,0:55:54.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这是国王的旨意 不得质疑\N{\fs16}and you are to do so without quarrel by order of your King.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.16,0:56:10.87,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,遵命 陛下\N{\fs16}Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.05,0:57:11.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,父亲\N{\fs16}Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.48,0:57:17.31,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,贝勒里恩是最后一个见证过\N{\fs16}Balerion was the last living creature
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.40,0:57:20.02,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,末日浩劫之前的瓦雷利亚的生物\N{\fs16}to have seen Old Valyria before the Doom.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.73,0:57:24.78,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,见证过它的伟大与阴暗\N{\fs16}Its greatness and its flaws.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.32,0:57:27.61,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当你凝视龙的时候 看到了什么？\N{\fs16}When you look at the dragons, what do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.24,0:57:29.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fs16}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.37,0:57:32.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,自从母亲葬礼后你再没和我说过一句话\N{\fs16}You haven't spoken a word to me since Mother's funeral
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.33,0:57:33.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而现在你派御林铁卫来……\N{\fs16}and now you send your Kingsguard down...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.91,0:57:35.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,回答我\N{\fs16}Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.92,0:57:39.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这很重要\N{\fs16}It's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.88,0:57:41.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你看到了什么？\N{\fs16}What do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.18,0:57:51.93,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,- 我感觉就像看到了我们自己 - 告诉我\N{\fs16}- I suppose I see us. - Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.85,0:57:56.77,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,每个人都说坦格利安比凡人更接近诸神\N{\fs16}Everyone says Targaryens are closer to gods than to men
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.85,0:57:59.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但他们那么说是因为我们的龙\N{\fs16}but they say that because of our dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.11,0:58:03.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,没有龙 我们泯然众人\N{\fs16}Without them, we're just like everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.19,0:58:11.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那种以为我们能控制龙的观念 只是假象\N{\fs16}The idea that we control the dragons is an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.62,0:58:16.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙的力量不是凡人可以随意玩弄操控的\N{\fs16}They're a power man should never have trifled with.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.04,0:58:20.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,它带来了瓦雷利亚末日浩劫\N{\fs16}One that brought Valyria its doom.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.88,0:58:23.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果我们不审视自己的历史 它也会给我们带来同样的后果\N{\fs16}If we don't mind our own histories, it will do the same to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.67,0:58:27.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,坦格利安必须明白这一点 才能成为国王……\N{\fs16}Targaryen must understand this to be King...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.59,0:58:29.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,……或者女王\N{\fs16}or Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.14,0:58:35.97,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉 雷妮拉\N{\fs16}I'm sorry, Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.77,0:58:39.69,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,自从你出生以来 我浪费了很多时光\N{\fs16}I have wasted the years since you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.77,0:58:41.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一直苦苦求子\N{\fs16}wanting for a son.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.41,0:58:55.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你继承了你母亲最好的一面\N{\fs16}You are the very best of your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.50,0:59:00.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我坚信 我知道她也坚信\N{\fs16}And I believe it, I know she did
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.92,0:59:03.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你会成为一位伟大的女王\N{\fs16}that you could be a great ruling queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.46,0:59:05.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙是你的继承人\N{\fs16}Daemon is your heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.50,0:59:09.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,戴蒙不是国王的料子\N{\fs16}Daemon was not made to wear the crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.76,0:59:11.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但我相信你是\N{\fs16}But I believe that you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.30,0:59:15.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,瓦列利安家族的科利斯\N{\fs16}Corlys of House Velaryon
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.39,0:59:19.52,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,潮汐之主 潮头岛伯爵\N{\fs16}Lord of the Tides and Master of Driftmark.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.60,0:59:22.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我 科利斯·瓦列利安\N{\fs16}I, Corlys Velaryon
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.90,0:59:25.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,潮汐之主 潮头岛伯爵\N{\fs16}Lord of the Tides and Master of Driftmark
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.07,0:59:28.07,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,承诺忠于韦赛里斯国王\N{\fs16}promise to be faithful to King Viserys
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.15,0:59:31.15,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,和他任命的继承人雷妮拉公主\N{\fs16}and his named heir, the Princess Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.24,0:59:33.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我向他们宣誓效忠\N{\fs16}I pledge fealty to them
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.36,0:59:35.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,尽忠护主 竭力御敌\N{\fs16}and shall defend them against all enemies
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.66,0:59:38.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一片忠心 绝无欺瞒\N{\fs16}in good faith and without deceit.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.54,0:59:45.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,誓言为证 新旧诸神\N{\fs16}I swear this by the old gods and the new.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.30,0:59:50.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这不是小事 雷妮拉\N{\fs16}This is no trivial gesture, Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.01,0:59:53.09,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,龙鞍是一码事\N{\fs16}A dragon's saddle is one thing
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.18,0:59:56.35,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但铁王座才是全国最危险的位置\N{\fs16}but the Iron Throne is the most dangerous seat in the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.22,0:59:59.18,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我 霍巴特·海塔尔伯爵\N{\fs16}I, Lord Hobert Hightower
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.27,1:00:01.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,南境灯塔 学城守护者\N{\fs16}Beacon of the South, Defender of the Citadel
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.68,1:00:03.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,旧镇之音\N{\fs16}and Voice of Oldtown
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.27,1:00:05.98,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,承诺忠于韦赛里斯国王\N{\fs16}promise to be faithful to King Viserys
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.06,1:00:09.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,和他任命的继承人雷妮拉公主\N{\fs16}and his named heir, the Princess Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.07,1:00:13.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我向他们宣誓效忠\N{\fs16}I pledge fealty to them
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.65,1:00:15.62,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,尽忠护主 竭力御敌\N{\fs16}and shall defend them against all enemies
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.70,1:00:18.41,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一片忠心 绝无欺言\N{\fs16}in good faith and without deceit.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.20,1:00:22.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,誓言为证 新旧诸神\N{\fs16}I swear this by the old gods and the new.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.13,1:00:30.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伸手\N{\fs16}Give me your hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.14,1:00:47.19,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我 博蒙德·拜拉席恩\N{\fs16}I, Boremund Baratheon
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.19,1:00:51.73,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,承诺忠于韦赛里斯国王\N{\fs16}promise to be faithful to King Viserys.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.61,1:00:57.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我还有事得告诉你\N{\fs16}There's something else that I need to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.32,1:00:59.37,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,你理解起来可能有些困难\N{\fs16}It might be difficult for you to understand
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.45,1:01:01.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但一定要仔细听着\N{\fs16}but you must hear it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.12,1:01:03.66,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我们的历史\N{\fs16}Our histories
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.75,1:01:06.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,他们说 伊耿从龙石岛眺望黑水湾对岸\N{\fs16}they tell us that Aegon looked across the Blackwater from Dragonstone
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.87,1:01:09.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,看见了一块静待主人的丰饶土地\N{\fs16}saw a rich land ripe for the capture.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.80,1:01:13.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,但驱使他征服的不只是野心\N{\fs16}But ambition alone is not what drove him to conquest.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.88,1:01:16.30,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,那是一个梦\N{\fs16}It was a dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.88,1:01:19.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,正如丹妮思预见到瓦雷里亚的末日\N{\fs16}And just as Daenys foresaw the end of Valyria
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.22,1:01:22.01,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿预见了人类世界的末日\N{\fs16}Aegon foresaw the end of the world of men.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.93,1:01:27.81,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,它始于遥远的北方袭来的可怕凛冬\N{\fs16}'Tis to begin with a terrible winter gusting out of the distant north.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.90,1:01:31.23,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我 瑞肯·史塔克 临冬城公爵\N{\fs16}I, Rickon Stark, Lord of Winterfell...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.32,1:01:34.74,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿看到寒风带来的终极黑暗\N{\fs16}Aegon saw absolute darkness riding on those winds.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.82,1:01:38.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,而栖身其中的东西 会催毁生者的世界\N{\fs16}And whatever dwells within will destroy the world of the living.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.03,1:01:42.28,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,当大寒冬来临的时候 雷妮拉\N{\fs16}When this Great Winter comes, Rhaenyra
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.37,1:01:44.91,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,所有维斯特洛人都该挺身抗击\N{\fs16}all of Westeros must stand against it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.20,1:01:46.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,如果人类世界要生存下去\N{\fs16}And if the world of men is to survive
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.62,1:01:49.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,就必须有一位坦格利安坐上铁王座\N{\fs16}a Targaryen must be seated on the Iron Throne.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.63,1:01:51.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,一位国王或者女王\N{\fs16}A king or queen
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.42,1:01:55.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,强大到足以团结王国对抗寒冷和黑暗\N{\fs16}strong enough to unite the realm against the cold and the dark.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.63,1:02:00.59,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,伊耿把这个梦称作“冰与火之歌”\N{\fs16}Aegon called his dream "The Song of Ice and Fire."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.39,1:02:04.56,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,这个秘密\N{\fs16}This secret
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.60,1:02:08.44,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,从伊耿时代起 就在国王和王储间口口相传\N{\fs16}it's been passed from king to heir since Aegon's time.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.06,1:02:12.40,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,现在你必须保证会传承秘密\N{\fs16}Now you must promise to carry it
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.07,1:02:14.57,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,守护秘密\N{\fs16}and protect it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.45,1:02:19.24,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,答应我 雷妮拉\N{\fs16}Promise me this, Rhaenyra.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.74,1:02:25.12,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,答应我\N{\fs16}Promise me.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.92,1:02:36.34,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,我 韦赛里斯·坦格利安一世\N{\fs16}I, Viserys Targaryen, first of his name
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.88,1:02:41.64,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,安达尔人 洛伊拿人和先民的国王\N{\fs16}King of the Andals, and the Rhoynar, and the First Men
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.47,1:02:46.60,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,七国统治者暨全境守护者\N{\fs16}Lord of the Seven Kingdoms, and Protector of the Realm
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.60,1:02:49.10,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,特此任命\N{\fs16}do hereby name
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.89,1:02:51.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,雷妮拉·坦格利安\N{\fs16}Rhaenyra Targaryen
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.02,1:02:54.32,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,为龙石岛公主\N{\fs16}Princess of Dragonstone
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.40,1:02:56.94,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,暨铁王座继承人\N{\fs16}and heir to the Iron Throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:28.30,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,345)}你在做什么 叔叔？\N{\fs16}Sparo drīvose gaomā, kepus?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:30.50,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,345)}随意坐坐\N{\fs16}Ñuhoso dēman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:33.43,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,345)}说不定哪天这就是我的椅子了\N{\fs16}Kesy ñuhys dēmavos māzīlariot sinilus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:35.85,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,345)}除非你想被处以煽动叛国罪\N{\fs16}Lo hen pāleknot statilūks, daor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.10,0:10:39.64,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,345)}你好久没来宫廷了\N{\fs16}Hen sȳndrāzmā qurdalbri imastō daor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.81,0:10:41.14,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs16}Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.27,0:10:43.98,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,345)}宫廷里无聊透顶\N{\fs16}Qurdalbar gierī tegenkor issa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.65,0:10:47.02,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,345)}那你为什么还回来？\N{\fs16}Sepār vēzo gō skoro syt āmastā?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:50.99,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,345)}我听说你父亲要以我的名义举办一场比武大会\N{\fs16}Kepa aōha yno syt kōttion pradilas, ryptan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.28,0:10:53.20,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,345)}那是为他的继承人举办的比武大会\N{\fs16}Kōttion dāranno syt issa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.87,0:10:56.83,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,345)}这不就是我的意思嘛\N{\fs16}Heksīr ȳdratan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:10:59.83,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,345)}他的新继承人\N{\fs16}Dāranno zȳho arlio syt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:03.70,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,345)}除非你母亲生下一个儿子\N{\fs16}Iā aōha muña trēsi sikos,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.67,0:11:06.63,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,345)}你们被我缠定了\N{\fs16}iā jevo yrgoti zbērion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.75,0:11:09.05,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,345)}那我倒是希望能有个弟弟\N{\fs16}Sepār valonqri jaelinna.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.39,0:12:00.97,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,345)}真美\N{\fs16}Gevie.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.80,0:42:48.78,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,345)}我在想 我弟弟活着的那几个小时里\N{\fs16}Ñurho valonqro paghyro jēdunna,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.90,0:42:53.74,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,345)}父亲是否终于体会到了幸福\N{\fs16}lo tolijī kepa ñuha kirimvī rhēdos pendan...?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.07,0:42:55.66,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,345)}你父亲需要你\N{\fs16}Kepa aōha avy sīr
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.08,0:43:00.16,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,345)}比以往任何时候更甚\N{\fs16}ojūdo tubiro toliot jorrāelza.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.46,0:43:02.67,Subtitle_Valyrian,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,345)}但我永远都无法成为他的儿子\N{\fs16}Trēsy dōrī kesan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.61,0:02:41.50,Character_B,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\t(\fs24)\b1\fad(500,1000)\pos(360,300)}这是韦赛里斯一世在位的第九年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:41.50,Character_B,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\t(\fs24)\b1\fad(500,1000)\pos(360,330)}此时离疯王伊里斯过世
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.57,0:02:43.79,Character_B,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\t(\fs24)\b1\fad(5000,1000)\pos(315,330)}离
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:41.50,Character_B,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\t(\fs24)\b1\fad(500,1000)\pos(360,360)}及其女儿丹妮莉丝·坦格利安公主出生 还有172年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.57,0:02:43.79,Character_B,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\t(\fs24)\b1\fad(5000,1000)\pos(400,360)}                丹妮莉丝·坦格利安        出生 还有172年